            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Enriched titanium in the form of oxide was 400 mg.",
                "Due to the small contribution of 51Ti to the spectrum",
                "from the enriched sample a natural titanium sample",
                "was also used.",
                " Isotopic compositions (atomic %):",
                "  Isotope     Natural sample        Enriched sample",
                "   46              7.93               2.0+-0.1",
                "   47              7.28               1.8+-0.1",
                "   48             73.94              17.8+-0.2",
                "   49              5.51               2.0+-0.l",
                "   50              5.34               6.4+-0.2"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".The absolute intensity values in photons/100 neutron",
                " captures were obtained by normalizing the sum of the",
                " primary gamma rays to 100.",
                ".in the low energy anticoincidence spectrum, the",
                " intensity of 1167 keV line was normalized to 320 keV",
                " line from decay of Ti-51 (see FLAG)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FLAG": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                1.0
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " normalized to the 320 keV line from the 5.8 min",
                " decay of 51Ti to 51V, the intensity of which",
                " was set equal to 95.09%."
              ]
            }
          ],
